title: Let Dell do the heavy lifting with Dell ProDeploy
text:
Submitted by admin on 10/20/2015 @ 3:00 PM   Principled Technologies 
DURHAM, NC--(Marketwired - October 20, 2015) - Planning and deploying new solutions for your datacenter can be time-consuming -- and all that time could be better spent focusing on organizational demands and other support tasks. Principled Technologies found that using a Dell ProDeploy engineer to deploy new Dell hardware solutions was faster and more efficient than doing the job in-house. 
To learn more about how Dell ProDeploy can save your company time, read the full report at facts.pt/1KjGhOj .
